Prerequisites:
=============
    - your user 'student' should be able to do 'sudo' - simply add it to the
      group 'wheel'

ASSIGNMENT
==========
1) Find out what is causing the high CPU load on the system
2) Take necessary steps towards eliminating this CPU load
3) Make sure account 'test' can no longer be used for *any* malicious activity
    - user 'test' has some valuable data in their account, so you MUST NOT
      remove the account!
